==批评==

中国的部分互联网用户对网信办感到不快，并将其与中国的其他言論審查機構戲稱為“[[真理部|真理部]]”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=《中国数字时代》真理部指令专栏|url=http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/category/%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8/%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E9%83%A8%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/|access-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308111231/https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/category/%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8/%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E9%83%A8%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4|archive-date=2021-03-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年1月，网信办发布了一首名为《网信精神》的歌，被[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]称为“倒回颂扬政权的革命歌曲”。<ref>{{cite web|title=China's Internet Censorship Anthem Is Revealed, Then Deleted|url=http://sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/02/12/chinas-internet-censorship-anthem-is-revealed-then-deleted/|access-date=2021-10-14|date=2015-02-12|website=Sinosphere Blog|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908000204/http://sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/02/12/chinas-internet-censorship-anthem-is-revealed-then-deleted/|archive-date=2015-09-08|url-status=dead}}</ref>

网信办曾被指控策划对国外企业的[[网络攻击|网络攻击]]。2015年，反审查团体[[GreatFire|GreatFire]]提供了数据和报告，调查对多个国外网站的[[中间人攻击|中间人攻击]]，包括[[iCloud|iCloud]]、[[雅虎|Yahoo]]、[[微软|微软]]和[[Google|Google]]，认为只有网信办有“在中国骨干网进行全国范围内的攻击”的能力。<ref>{{Cite web|title=给鲁炜和中国网信办的公开信|url=https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2015/jan/open-letter-lu-wei-and-cyberspace-administration-china|access-date=2021-10-14|date=2015-01-26|website=GreatFire|archive-url=https://archive.today/20211013052129/https://zh.greatfire.org/blog/2015/1%E6%9C%88/%E7%BB%99%E9%B2%81%E7%82%9C%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E4%BF%A1%E5%8A%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%80%E4%BF%A1|archive-date=2021-10-13|quote=中国网信办没有对Outlook进行了中间人攻击，或者没有故意让其他人进行攻击，那请问您如何解释为何“敌对势力“能在过去两年中至少6次在中国骨干网进行全国范围内的攻击？|url-status=no}}</ref>Gibson 研究公司认为2015年[[对GitHub的审查和封锁#DDoS攻击|对GitHub的DDoS攻击]]和网信办的行动有关。攻击中[[百度|百度]]广告的[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]脚本被劫持，转移国外访问者的流量到[[GitHub|GitHub]]网站，来使其过载。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20150331/c31hack/|title=中国劫持百度广告流量攻击GitHub|date=2015-03-31|publisher=紐約時報|author=孟建国|accessdate=2021-10-14|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150510104223/http://cn.nytimes.com/china/20150331/c31hack/|archive-date=2015-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>Gibson 认为：“劫持发生在流量进入中国和流量到达百度服务器之间部分...这和过去的恶意行为一样，显示网信办与之直接相关。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Security Now! #501|url=https://www.grc.com/sn/sn-501-notes.pdf|author=Gibson Research Corporation|date=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906054445/https://www.grc.com/sn/sn-501-notes.pdf|archive-date=2015-09-06|quote=The tampering takes places someplace between when the traffic enters China and when it hits Baidu's servers, This is consistent with previous malicious actions and points to the Cyberspace Administration of China (CAC) being directly involved...|url-status=live}}</ref>

[[ProPublica|ProPublica]]和纽约时报在2020年的调查发现网信办系统地在社交媒体上审查关于[[2019冠状病毒病|新冠肺炎]]爆发的消息，对[[李文亮|李文亮]]的提及，并“安排了大量[[网络评论员|网络评论员]]，使用无关的闲聊来转移注意。”<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Zhong|first1=Raymond|last2=Mozur|first2=Paul|last3=Krolik|first3=Aaron|last4=Kao|first4=Jeff|date=2020-12-19|title=Leaked Documents Show How China's Army of Paid Internet Trolls Helped Censor the Coronavirus|work=[[ProPublica|ProPublica]]|url=https://www.propublica.org/article/leaked-documents-show-how-chinas-army-of-paid-internet-trolls-helped-censor-the-coronavirus|url-status=live|access-date=2021-10-14|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219101738/https://www.propublica.org/article/leaked-documents-show-how-chinas-army-of-paid-internet-trolls-helped-censor-the-coronavirus}}</ref>

